Class TwitterVideoDescription

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class TwitterVideoDescription
extends java.lang.Object
    Video description retrieved from Twitter.

    Optional Elements

    • location

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<videoDescription>
  <createdTimestamp>2005-11-26T05:00:42+0200</createdTimestamp>
  <location>
    <name>yzwIAymcUjnpEdyWkZnKbgNPVWzyRAyUrqtmkQPcEIhtdiXFCgGpnwJlsHajxmkm</name>
    <latitude>52.0</latitude>
    <longitude>-28.0</longitude>
  </location>
  <description>#obpTyl NkGJK2K #ZWzg QcV #q10Y #AbW2b0Y1 #JTng XlRjFU8C #6F8HC0 #SoOzx6 #4jH BdGYR FusgfR #07wC suhl2 jH6 #fUKwV 97f3Mo GRuMP9ak #cPZrn</description>
  <from>UYBqZBHaiCafHHfmXtNIwfRtfJYViQgQJXPItZqrhcXvLiVayCznFEaLKCuEJYTW</from>
</videoDescription>
